UFW security rules

allowing LAN zone rule (192.168.100.0/24 network) through ports 80(HTTP) and 443(HTTPS)
command - "sudo ufw allow from 192.168.100.0/24 to any port 80"
command - "sudo ufw allow from 192.168.100.0/24 to any port 443"

allowing SSH from LAN zone rule (192.168.100.0/24 network) through port 22(SSH)
command - "sudo ufw allow from 192.168.100.0/24 to any port 22"

allowing remote desktop from LAN zone rule (192.168.100.0/24 network) through port to any port 3389(rdp)
command - "sudo ufw allow from 192.168.100.0/24 to any port 3389"

allowing DNS from the WAN ip "8.8.8.8" through UDP port 53.
command - "sudo ufw allow from 8.8.8.8 to any port 53"


